    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a binding for the Extensible Messaging and Presence Protocol (XMPP) over a WebSocket transport layer.  A WebSocket binding for XMPP provides higher performance than the current HTTP binding for XMPP.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
